rows.label: qst202003_msg0001
rows.name:
So you're fetching firewood for Musubi,
eh?

rows.label: qst202003_msg0002
rows.name:
Tch, and here I was looking forward
to saying hello to her...

rows.label: qst202003_msg0004
rows.name:
Kidding, kidding. My humor's a little
on the dry side.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0005
rows.name:
Just head over to the scrap wood pile.
You'll find plenty of firewood there.
Help yourselves.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0006
rows.name:
Incidentally, how's the old man
keeping? Still his sprightly self?

rows.label: qst202003_msg0007
rows.name: Good to hear, good to hear.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0008
rows.name: I owe a lot to Mabon, way back when.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0009
rows.name:
He's Superbian, himself, but he moved
here to Trigo of his own accord.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0010
rows.name:
Up until recently, he was teaching
Gulan Drivers how to handle
themselves.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0011
rows.name:
But his body couldn't keep up with it.
Hell of a thing, old age.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0012
rows.name:
Anyway, I'd better let you go. Best
not keep Musubi waiting, eh?
